description:
&lt;p&gt;Providing quality, inspiring innovation and  delivering value is what we set out to achieve at Priory Healthcare. Enabling our patients with mental health difficulties to receive a truly integrated and holistic approach to their treatment, regardless of complexity or severity, thanks to the knowledge and expertise of our multidisciplinary clinical teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Priory Highbank Centre offers specialist cognitive care and rehabilitation for children and adults who have sustained a brain injury and is part of the Priory Group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a Registered General Nurse (at least 18 months post qualification), with clinical experience including leadership skills and an ability to mentor junior staff. The role will involve caring for adults with complex physical and functional needs, including tracheostomy and long term ventilation for which full training will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity within a highly specialised field for the right nurses to join a busy interdisciplinary team and enjoy new challenges in a fully supported role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The desired requirements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in general nursing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to embrace new learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compassionate advocate for patients with complex physical and cognitive impairment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to write comprehensive care plans and reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return, we can offer:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Autonomous practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with a committed, forward thinking and supportive interdisciplinary team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and opportunities for continuing professional development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributory pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid sick leave (after qualifying period)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to regular clinical supervision &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous annual leave entitlement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Subsidised meals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking, corporate benefit package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants will be subject to recruitment and selection procedures designed to emphasis the Unit&#39;s commitment to the safeguarding of it&#39;s service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be required to apply for a disclosure at the enhanced level from the Disclosure &amp; Barring Services, which will be paid for by the Priory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
